1) emerge -v '>=sys-apps/portage-2.0.51-r9'
2) emerge unmerge app-emulation/emul-linux-x86-glibc
3) rm /lib32 /usr/lib32 /usr/X11R6/lib32
4) emerge -v '>=sys-apps/baselayout-1.11.8-r1'
5) rm /etc/make.profile
6) ln -s /usr/portage/profiles/default-linux/amd64/2005.0 /etc/make.profile
7) cd /usr/tmp
8) wget http://dev.gentoo.org/~eradicator/grp/amd64/2005.0/glibc-2.3.4.20040808-r1.tbz2
9) emerge -v glibc-2.3.4.20040808-r1.tbz2
10) emerge -upv system
11) emerge -uv system

Note, The order is VERY important.
You MUST do every step even if you already have that version installed.  If
you don't, it might be bad for you!
